Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.04,0:01:45.68,MainStyle,,0255,0000,0000,,{\fad(1050,990)}{\a1\2a&HFF&}A Hot Wind and Violent Drive on Usui's Mountain Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Looks really bad.\NCan I make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:22.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If they can do it, there's no reason I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, almost rub the inside.\NGrip the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Obstacles.\NMove outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.  He isn't an ordinary\NRoad Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:24.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Otherwise we wouldn't have any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much longer\Nhe can keep up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't gotten serious yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This's tough.  I'm not driving\Nin my own style...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...I'm just copying their style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This isn't any different than a roller coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Because I'm not in my rhythm, this is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But if I get outrun now, I won't\Nbe able to catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've got to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:14.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Not knowing the course is a much\Ntougher handicap than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:21.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If I lose my concentration, I'll crash into\Nthe mountainside or fall off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:34.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Akina's famous Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't let us outrun him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:41.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The terror of Usui, where the corners appear\None after another, begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A right-hander's, next.\NIt's narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:57.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, but I can't let it pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If they can turn, I should be able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:23.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi said, if they can turn, he\Nshould be able to, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:29.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.\NWhat a simple idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his brain made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:36.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a great thing, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:39.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a skilled driver like him\Nwould think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:45.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless he loses control at a corner's\Nentrance, he can control the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be able to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But his opponent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:53.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mako and her Sil-Eighty, who knows everything\Nabout this mountain's passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be pushing her\Ncar to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:07:00.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Takumi'll have to enter\Ncorners at the same speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His first time on Usui's\Nunfamiliar passes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That gives me a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary to even think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:15.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  He'll need plenty of guts,\Nnot just technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He said his opponent is a Sil-Eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What's a Sil-Eighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's on my tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?  I'm driving fast enough, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are.\NYou're in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's right on my tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking into the mirror.\NIt'll disturb your rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:12.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm checking what's happening\Nbehind us, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to enjoy this.\NIt's a great battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, trust your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the best team on Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}If the frontrunner runs away from\Nthe chaser, the front wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:39.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}If not, switch positions and try again\Nuntil the game is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's a sudden death death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:46.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}With this rule, you should take\Nthe front for the first heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:51.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Yeah, there'll be a second heat,\Nso you'll have a chance to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Even if you lose in the second heat,\Nyou won't look too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'll take the rear for the first heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Think it over, Takumi.\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}This is my battle...\NLet me decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:17.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I chose the rear because\NI hate having somebody on my tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...but I didn't expect\Nit to be this hard.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0130,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:27.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The most difficult part of attacking\Nan unfamiliar course is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:31.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...the ability to decide\Na corner's entry speed.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.39,MainStyle,,0000,0242,0354,,{\fad(0,500)\fs18\frz1\bord1\4a&ff&}Theory of the Fastest on the Street
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The reason why Keisuke was defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and the reason Nakazato was passed\Nare essentially the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:54.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No matter how skilled a driver is, he can't\Nmatch one who drives hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If so, to defeat the Eight-Six on Akina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}With my hypothesis, I'll be able\Nto defeat him, even on Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:23.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:26.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I took a big gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:30.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Just a few centimeters difference\Nat the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:34.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and the speed difference causes\Na big gap at the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I scratched the bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I won't let it pull away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:05.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}A Road Racer grows by experiencing\Nmany terrifying moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:13.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}With extraordinary concentration\Nand trained driving technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:20.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and with my perfect suspension setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...he won't lose.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.25,0:11:28.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0400,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Nagano Prefecture\NKaruizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the race already settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know until they return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:39.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nit's too unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,B...but, Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:46.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so far, none of the races have\Nbeen easy for Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:50.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato's 32 was monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:56.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And the gumtape death match with that\NShoji guy was his first try at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:00.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing was always on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They all happened on Akina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...where Takumi has driven every day\Nfor the last five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:13.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, is the course\Ndifference that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:18.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be different if he had\Ndriven here a few times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is his very first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:26.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:29.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've been wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:36.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the girl sitting next to Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?  Even if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She caught my attention, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:45.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She got in the car so naturally, even though\Nthey were going to race.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:51.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know her well, but she's been\Nher best friend since childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:55.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they've driven together\Nsince they were beginners...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they perfected\Ntheir driving skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:08.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's like a rally navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, Takumi's in an even\Nmore difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NTakumi shouldn't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:24.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But with a good navigator sitting next to Mako,\Nshe can concentrate on driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Obstacle before the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid it and close the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's still keeping up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How can he follow us\Nat this high pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Mako is in the best condition,\Nbut he's still on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:40.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako, C-121 is near.\NLet's settle this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can skid from the\Nentry of the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:50.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show him what we can do at the\Nmost difficult corner on Mt. Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show him my car skid from\Nthe entry to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:15:01.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has cleared the corner\Nat my entry speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't Mako and Sayuki come tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NI haven't seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the Sil-Eighty's drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This C-121 corner is the highlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than just difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:47.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can skid from the entry to the exit,\Nyou're considered highly skilled on Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:51.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're good on Usui, you're\Nthe best wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:55.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to enter the corner at\Nhigh speed with lots of guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:59.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...or you'll lose speed, and your drift\Nwon't last until the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone fails on their first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you get used to it,\Nyou can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a few can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:12.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Mako's Sil-Eighty enters\Nthe corner at full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:17.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how fast she goes,\Nbut no one can copy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's... coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The squeals are so loud.\NSomeone's really pushing it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Sil-Eighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako and Sayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a car behind it.\NWho is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A...are they racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that an Eight-Six?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No oncoming traffic.\NLet's show off, Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:04.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They dove into the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:30.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he must be stupid, entering the\Ncorner at the same speed as Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know how difficult C-121 is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't clear the corner\Nwith only courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:51.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's got nerve entering the\Ncorner right behind Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:56.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Once you enter this corner at that speed,\Nyou can't use any tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:18:01.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The middle section of the C-121 is wide,\Nbut the exit is extremely narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:06.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There appear to be many lines you\Ncan take, but there's only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...to stay on that line on your first try?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Im...impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He cleared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's driving that Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be Akina's Eight-Six\Nthey've been talking about lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I've got goose bumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}H...how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:09.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The difficulty of four-wheel drift\Nat very high speed is ultra D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even with all her experience, Mako missed\Nthe entry by five centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But he... he controlled the car\Nto follow the ideal line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}We can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}We chose a totally outclassing\Nmonster as our opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:51.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't skid\Nso much in this corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me that before\Nwe entered the corner, Sayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap out of it!\NIt's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it yet, Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six behind us is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to win with our skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!\NYou always talk big!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The race isn't over, but\Nyou're ready to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't depend on you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that the Eight-Six was extraordinary\Nfrom the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided this race would be my last!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So unless we try our best,\NI won't be satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have gotten so timid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:54.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!  You're like baggage\Nin the passenger seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:21:00.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're only ballast, worsening\Nthe power to weight ratio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}She's one of those people who changes\Npersonality behind the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,HOW CAN YOU CALL ME BALLAST?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:08.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'VE GOT A NICE BODY, AND I'M NOT\NCHUBBY OR FAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:10.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a 49 kg handicap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,47 KG!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:17.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've said that,\NI can't stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Mako!\NDrive like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:25.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it.{what I wanted.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:29.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn hard, as if you were going to hit\Nthe cliff in the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sayuki.
