Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.40,0:21:56.91,SongWings,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Wings of fire, hirogaru kono sora wo kakemeguru\N{\fnTahoma\fs18\i0\c&H808080&}Wings of fire. We fly around in the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm getting better, even while I'm\Ndesperately following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can feel the rhythm\Nof this mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:06.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can drive in my own rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:11.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}There are a few corners to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:13.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But I won't drop my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll push harder and\Nharder till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't let this be regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:21.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}For the pride of the best on Usui!
