Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:34.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Mr. Bunta, does Takumi have a chance of\Nwinning the battle against the Sil-Eighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:36.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}"Who knows...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:38.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a tofu shop owner, not a fortuneteller.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:40.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Oh, can I have Ganmo and fried tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:43.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Eight-Six I've thoroughly tuned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:45.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No car can outrun my car on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:47.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's up to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:49.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait and you'll see next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:50.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:52.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I'll buy both soft and hard tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:55.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Initial D,\N"Race-Settling Super Drift."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.10,0:24:56.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you see it.
