Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.09,0:25:00.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0190,,Race-Settling Super Drift
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't miss it!